@startuml
!include _yunlink_protocol_theme.iuml
title Command Result Derivation State Machine

[*] --> Validate : inbound command

state Validate <<Transit>> {
}

Validate --> Failed : no active session
Validate --> Failed : no authority
Validate --> Failed : ttl expired
Validate --> Failed : target != kEntity
Validate --> Failed : unsupported command
Validate --> Received : validation passed

state Received <<ActiveState>>
state Accepted <<ActiveState>>
state InProgress <<Transit>>
state Succeeded <<Terminal>>
state Failed <<Risk>>

Received --> Accepted : ROS publish ok
Received --> Failed : ROS publish failed
Accepted --> InProgress : FSM enters execution state
Accepted --> Failed : session invalidated
Accepted --> Failed : authority lost
Accepted --> Failed : execution timeout
InProgress --> Succeeded : FSM convergence rule hit
InProgress --> Failed : session invalidated
InProgress --> Failed : authority lost
InProgress --> Failed : execution timeout

Succeeded --> [*]
Failed --> [*]
@enduml
